The dentist will provide care to our patients, regulate patient flow within the office, and report to the Chief Clinical Officer and Senior Director of Practice Success. The General Dentist will partner with the Administrative Lead and Regional Operations Manager to maintain, implement, and support practice standards.

We are looking to hire an Associate General Dentist for our busy Nashua practice. Our office has a great low-stress, family oriented environment where many of our patients have been coming to us for over 50 years. We have a very low turnover rate with our longest employee working over 25 years! We love bringing in new talent to join our team where everyone has a good work ethic and works to promote the overall well-being of the practice and our patients.
Our office currently provides treatment to patients of all ages and we offer a wide range of services including dental hygiene, restorations, dentures, endodontics, simple extractions, orthodontics and cosmetic treatments.
We are currently seeking an Associate who will be a good compliment to our team and who is comfortable with all aspects of general dentistry. We offer healthcare, dental benefits, and 401K for qualified candidates. To learn more about our office, please visit our website at www.landmarkdentalnashua.com. To apply please submit your resume and cover letter.

ABOUT US
HealthNet of Rock County is a free and charitable clinic serving Rock County individuals who are low-income, uninsured, or underinsured for medical, dental, vision and behavioral health services. HealthNet of Rock County, Inc. opened in 1994 as a 501(c)3 non-profit organization through the result of a needs assessment that identified a lack of affordable healthcare as one of the major problems in Rock County.
HealthNet of Rock County, Inc. seeks a driven, motivated part-time General Dentist (8 hours per week) who will help the organization make a significant difference in the community. The ideal candidate must have excellent interpersonal skills with an interest in providing high-quality personalized care to patients in a community-based care setting.
